<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Microsoft JhengHei', sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .container { text-align: center; padding: 40px; }
        h1 { font-size: 4rem; color: #E74C3C; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        a { color: #E74C3C; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p><%= message %></p>
        <p>抱歉造成不便，請稍後再試</p>
        <a href="/">返回首頁</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>